MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the DG8 postcode area of Newton Stewart. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 03.03am. Repairs are taking longer than expected due to onsite difficulties and our team are now working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 07.00am. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 04:54am on Monday, 26 April 2021
